<HL>
   Norwest Corp. Buy-Back
</HL>
<DATE>
09/27/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
<CO>
   NOB
</CO>
<IN>
CENTRAL U.S. BANKS (BAC)
BANKS (BNK)
BUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK)
</IN>
<LP>
   MINNEAPOLIS -- Norwest Corp. authorized the buy-back of up
to five million shares, or nearly 5%, of its common stock
outstanding.
   The diversified financial services company said the shares
will be used to meet needs of various employee savings, stock
ownership and shareholder dividend reinvestment plans, and
for other corporate purposes.
</LP>
