   ---
   Correction
                                                                                                       

   The firm that did a survey on high-yield bonds mentioned
Thursday in the editorial-page feature "The War Against
Wealth" is High Yield Research Partners of New York. The name
was misstated.
   (WSJ Sept. 28, 1990)
</TEXT>
